window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Will I sacrifice my heart to save my home?</b></p> <p>War has finally come to the Mists. The Murk have invaded, and if they have their way, the men I love and all the other fae in the place I now call home will fall before their twisted magic.</p> <p>I may be only human, but I won't let my lovers fight alone. I've proven again and again that I'm more than a cure for their curse. I'm not a tool but a wild card our enemies still don't fully understand. But, our only chance at victory may come at a cost too high for me to bear. What if winning means destroying the bonds that have made my life worth living?</p> <p><b><i>Heart of the Mists </i></b><b>is the ninth and final book in Bound to the Fae, a new paranormal romance series featuring possessive shifters, dangerous fae politics, and a wounded heroine finding her strength.</b></p>"; 
